  <name>SysD Manager</name>
  <summary>A GUI to manage systemd units</summary>
  <!--   <icon type="stock">io.github.plrigaux.sysd-manager</icon> -->
  <description>
    <p>This application exists to allow user to manage their systemd units via a GUI. Not only
      are you able to make changes to the enablement and running status of each of the units, but
      you will also be able to view and modify their unit files and check the journal logs. </p>
  </description>
